FBIS3-27744 "dreas020_n_94007" FBIS-EAS-94-020 Document Type:Daily Report 31 Jan 1994 Vietnam U.S. Radio Free Asia, Human Rights Criticized Foreign Ministry on Senate Vote BK2901103294 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam in English 1000 GMT 29 Jan 94 BK2901103294 Hanoi Voice of Vietnam Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] A spokesman for the Vietnamese Foreign Ministry said the (intention) by the U.S. Senate to set up a radio service called Liberal Asia Radio is not welcomed in Asia. Asian people understand the move is aimed at imposing U.S. views and interfering in internal affairs causing instability in Asia.
